prodNameC: 貝克曼庫爾特 亞瑟斯德國麻疹免疫球蛋白G試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Access Rubella IgG Reagent:
R1a: paramagnetic particles coated with rubella (strain HPV 77) sucrose gradient purified antigen suspended in TRIS buffered saline, with bovine serum albumin (BSA).
R1b: TRIS buffered saline with surfactant, BSA.
R1c: Mouse monoclonal anti-human IgG antibody (clone 125 A 15) - alkaline phosphatase (bovine) conjugate in TRIS buffered saline with surfactant, glycerol, BSA, mouse proteins.
Access Rubella IgG Calibrators:
S0: Equine serum with 0 IU/mL anti-rubella IgG.
S1，S2，S3，S4，S5: Equine serum and human serum containing approximately 10, 25, 50, 200 and 500 IU/mL of human anti-rubella IgG.
Access Rubella IgG QC:
QC1: Human serum with <0.1% sodium azide; contains no detectable level of anti-rubella IgG.
QC2: Human serum with <0.1% sodium azide; contains a low level of anti-rubella IgG (target mean of 22-43 IU/mL).
